data.description: Waterfront home on .89 acres with your own private boat dock!  Don't miss out on this charming, brick Cape Cod home located in Carolina Trace. Four bedrooms and three bathrooms. Enjoy STUNNING views of the lake from the family room, dining room, kitchen and upstairs guest room.  The kitchen has quartz countertops and stainless-steel appliances.  Updated carpet in all four bedrooms and on stairs.  Updated premium LVP floors installed over original hardwood floors.  Updated Primary bathroom, as well as fresh paint in all bathrooms. A new gas fireplace insert in family room.  Retaining walls added in front yard and bricks in walkway re-laid. Bonus room over garage. Updated floor in garage and breezeway.  Large, landscaped lot with mature hardwoods, Dogwood trees, Camelia trees and Azalea bushes.  Sit on the backyard swing enjoying gorgeous lake views and wildlife. There is a paved golf cart path which will take you to the bottom lawn at the lake.  Within walking distance to country club. Contact Carolina Trace Country Club for various membership types.
